Volume = {28},
Number = {1},
Pages = {1006-1009},
Month = {JAN-FEB},
Abstract = {With the rapid development of economy and technologies in our country,
   the production of clothing has changed a lot. The type and quantity of
   the fashion design have a large range of growth, and among them, 3D
   garment design has attracted people's attention. Based on this, 3D
   garment design based on component library and interactive genetic
   algorithm and its evaluation were studied in this paper. First of all,
   the data structure and generation of garment parts are introduced; then,
   coding based on component pointers were introduced; finally, the process
   of 3D garment design based on component library and interactive genetic
   algorithm was introduced in detail. The test results show that the
   application of 3D garment method based on component library and
   interactive genetic algorithm is more practical and reasonable.},
